  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 14th level, the divine power that fuels your rage allows you to shrug off fatal blows.</p><p>While you're raging, having 0 hit points doesn't knock you unconscious. You still must make death saving throws, and you suffer the normal effects of taking damage while at 0 hit points. However, if you would die due to failing death saving throws, you don't die until your rage ends, and you die then only if you still have 0 hit points.</p>",
